column1: NOTE: Table reads (for US Totals):  Of all 30,650 public schools with grades 7 and 8, 18,258 (59.6%) offered Algebra I classes.
Data reported in this table represent 100.0% of responding schools.

SOURCE: U.S. Department of Education, Office for Civil Rights, Civil Rights Data Collection, 2013-14, available at http://ocrdata.ed.gov. Data notes are available at https://ocrdata.ed.gov/Downloads/Data-Notes-2015-16-CRDC.pdf.
